	"name": "Tools",
	"description": "§b§lRefractor Mirror§r\n- Holding this item in your main hand or off-hand allows you to use some of your active abilities, like §e[FTL]§r, §e[FTL:§r §eBlink]§r and §e[Veil§r §eof§r §eIllusions]§r.\n \n§b§lPhoton Regulator§r:\n- Using this item on Photon Coordinators or a Lodestone allows you to configure the coordinates and mode of your §e[FTL:§r §eWarp]§r ability. This item also deals increased damage with aerial attacks.\n \n§b§lReturn Shard§r:\n- Consuming this item allows any player to reverse their latest §e[FTL:§r §eWarp]§r teleportation, and sets their Y coordinate to 320. This item can be crafted by anyone.\n \n§b§lCrystalline Emblem§r:\n- Using this item when your §5[Trapped§r §5Light]§r is full allows you to unleash a blinding flash of light after one and a half seconds, which depletes your §5[Trapped§r §5Light]§r. Creatures that can see you are affected by §5[True§r §5Blindness]§r for 30 seconds. Right clicking this item while sneaking will toggle §5[Crystalline§r §5Movement]§r.",
